Description: The `bbou` suite of packages are designed to allow analysis
    (`bbouretro` and `bboutools`) and simulation (`bbousims`) of Boreal
    Caribou survival and recruitment data ('bboudata') to estimate
    population growth rates. A shiny app is also available (`bboushiny`).
